definitions.definition: One who or that which turns.
A person who turns and shapes wood etc. on a lathe .
A kitchen utensil used for turning food.
( zoology ) A variety of pigeon ; a tumbler .
( cricket ) A very dry pitch on which the ball will turn with ease.

main_definition: One who or that which turns.

definitions.definition: ( sports ) An acrobat or gymnast , especially ( historical ) a member of the German Turnvereine , German-American gymnastic clubs that also served as nationalist political groups.
